Q: 查询在16 L Ranch停场的所有公务机及其注册号
SQL:
SELECT
    arr_icao AS icao_code,
    registration
FROM
    zts_plane_status
WHERE
    status = 0
    AND pure_reg IN (
        SELECT
            LOWER(REPLACE(REPLACE(registration, ' ', ''), '-', ''))
        FROM
            dc_aircraft
        WHERE
            delete_tag = 0
    )
    AND arr_icao ="16TT" COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci;

            delete_tag = 0
    )
    AND arr_icao ="HEBL" COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci;

Q: 查询在Abumumbazi停场的所有公务机及其注册号
SQL:
SELECT
    arr_icao AS icao_code,
    registration
FROM
    zts_plane_status
WHERE
    status = 0
    AND pure_reg IN (
        SELECT
            LOWER(REPLACE(REPLACE(registration, ' ', ''), '-', ''))
        FROM
            dc_aircraft
        WHERE
            delete_tag = 0
    )
    AND arr_icao ="FZFE" COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci;
